<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <meta name="robots" content="noindex,nofollow" />
    <title>Client Access Code | <%= appName %></title>
    <style>
      :root { color-scheme: dark; font-family: Inter, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif; }
      * { box-sizing: border-box; }
      body { display: grid; min-width: 320px; min-height: 100vh; margin: 0; place-items: center; background: radial-gradient(ellipse 60% 42% at 50% -10%, rgba(255,255,255,.04), transparent 70%), #09090b; color: #f5f5f4; }
      main { width: min(100% - 32px,520px); }
      .card { border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08); border-radius: 18px; background: linear-gradient(145deg,rgba(25,25,29,.96),rgba(14,14,17,.94)); box-shadow: 0 28px 90px rgba(0,0,0,.5); padding: 30px; }
      .eyebrow { margin: 0 0 7px; color: #71717a; font-size: 9px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: .15em; text-transform: uppercase; }
      h1 { margin: 0 0 8px; font-size: 24px; letter-spacing: -.03em; }
      p { color: #a1a1aa; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6; }
      .code-box { margin: 18px 0; padding: 16px; border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.12); border-radius: 12px; background: rgba(0,0,0,.35); word-break: break-all; font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, Menlo, Consolas, monospace; font-size: 15px; color: #f5f5f4; }
      .warn { border: 1px solid rgba(250,204,21,.28); background: rgba(250,204,21,.08); color: #fde68a; border-radius: 10px; padding: 10px 12px; font-size: 12px; margin-bottom: 4px; }
      a.btn { display: inline-block; margin-top: 18px; border: 0; border-radius: 11px; background: #f5f5f4; box-shadow: 0 6px 18px rgba(0,0,0,.35); color: #0a0a0b; font: 750 13px inherit; text-decoration: none; padding: 12px 18px; }
      a.btn:hover { background: #ffffff; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <main>
      <section class="card">
        <p class="eyebrow">Client Access Code</p>
        <h1><%= accountLabelText %></h1>
        <p>Share this access code with your client through a secure channel (not email/chat that CHANTER staff can see later, if possible). It logs into their portal at <strong>/client/autoposter/login</strong> — nothing else.</p>
        <div class="warn">This code is shown once. It is not stored in plain text — if lost, generate a new one (this invalidates the old one).</div>
        <div class="code-box"><%= code %></div>
        <a class="btn" href="/private/autoposter">Back to dashboard</a>
      </section>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
